Implications
\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
1.
 
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{n}\overset{d}{\rightarrow}Y$
\end_inset

 iff 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{E}f(Y_{n})\rightarrow\mathbb{E}f(Y)\forall$
\end_inset

 bounded, continuous f.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
