\begin_inset Formula $\lfloor\gamma n\rfloor'th$
\end_inset

 order statistics for 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{1},X_{2},...,X_{n}$
\end_inset

.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $F(\theta)=\gamma,$
\end_inset

